column1: Baby Barnaby's////So many people have already raved about Baby Barnaby's and their delicious food so I'll keep it short. Baby Barnaby's is a super cute and tiny cafe known for its brunch. It's very popular
column2: with lines that wrap around the block on weekends
column3: so be sure to get here early and sign up on that clipboard! I ordered the Green Eggs and substituted the toast for biscuits and mm the dish was wonderful. The veggies added flavor and texture to the eggs
column7: and the sausage tasted unique and yummy. The only small thing that bothered me was that everything had salty undertones
column9: but it's miniscule. The servers were so friendly and I'll definitely be back to try all the dishes on the menu!
